# Betting (Non-Remote) - Money Laundering and Terrorist Financing Risk Assessment 2023

**Overall Risk Rating:** High (Off-course) / Medium (On-course)

## Summary

Non-remote betting presents varying risk levels depending on location. Off-course betting shops are rated as high risk due to cash transactions, gaming machines, and accessibility to multiple premises. On-course betting at racecourses is rated as medium risk, with lower transaction volumes and different operational characteristics reducing some vulnerabilities.

## Inherent Risks by Vulnerability Category

### Operator Control Vulnerabilities

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk | Applies To |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|------------|
| Operators failing to comply with prevention of money laundering and terrorist financing legislation and guidance | High (3) | High (3) | High (9) | No change | Off-course only |
| Operators failing to comply with prevention of money laundering and terrorist financing legislation and guidance | Medium (2) | Medium (2) | Medium (4) | No change | On-course only |
| Lack of effective customer interaction resulting in a failure to prevent and/or detect Money Laundering or Terrorist financing (ML/TF) | Medium (2) | High (3) | High (6) | No change | Off-course only |
| Lack of effective customer interaction resulting in a failure to prevent and/or detect ML or TF | Medium (2) | Medium (2) | Medium (4) | No change | On-course only |
| Inadequate or lack of 'know your customer' (KYC) checks resulting in criminals laundering criminal proceeds | High (3) | High (3) | High (9) | No change | Off-course only |
| Inadequate or lack of KYC checks resulting in criminals laundering criminal proceeds | Medium (2) | Medium (2) | Medium (4) | No change | On-course only |
| Third party business relationships and business investors | Medium (2) | High (3) | High (6) | New risk | Off-course only |
| On-course bookmakers providing unlicensed gambling activities (e.g., accepting bets over the phone without required ancillary betting licence) | Low (1) | Medium (2) | Medium (2) | No change | On-course only |

