| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk | Applies To |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|------------|
| Betting operations being acquired by organised crime to launder criminal proceeds | Low (1) | High (3) | Medium (3) | No change | Off-course only |
